artificialFastqGenerator

Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • artificialFastqGenerator.Main

  • public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for checking whether the user's command is valid, and if it is, creating instances of the ArtificialFastqGenerator class in order to generate fastq files.
